Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到小文了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌真像個男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  美歌女孩子氣十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們二人同體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  通過認證
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以把這種東西對著別人喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  要不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫…醫生  救護車…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫醫生沒用的  醫院也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  他是美川煌老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開  給我打開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慫恿我們家文歌的是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報上名字來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  對不起  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您在此稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳被炒啦  小心我讓妳在這行混不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  嘴角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  反正我本來就不被看好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況  醫生看了肯定會引起大騷亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  美川她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可被打中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫救護車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杖在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是杖啦  是卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比通報到上面  事情鬧大了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克…風？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杖在說話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧  這個卡娜卡是活的還可以說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳能理解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於妳的事  還有其它的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於長大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指文伽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長大的郵遞員  還能有其他人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員都是死者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以時間保持停止  成長也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以永遠也不會死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說和我們不同  那孩子的年齡和外表相符
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說她還是個孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做郵遞員還早得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經是一個叫做美川文歌的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  可是醫院裡的那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  三年前開始一直昏迷  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽文歌說到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說完後再提問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續吧  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親是美川煌  剛才朝我開槍的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我出生後立刻和父親離婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛澤美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女演員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和名字一樣  是個美女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該和別人結婚了  住在海外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我不知道媽媽愛澤美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  美川煌撫養我長大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  做得很容易入口了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你  啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌曾經是個溫柔的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我曾經最喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也愛著身為分身的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  是上藝術課的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得何時  為什麼開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後的世界如同冰雪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何活物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有草  沒有花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有四季  什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  死後的世界是美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被統一的簡單顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有蟲  沒有細菌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何污垢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終極潔淨  無垢  干淨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}綺麗(kirei)在日語中有『干淨』和『美麗』意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干淨?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是美麗的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗  竟說是美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骯髒的黑色眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛榮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌老師為什麼要做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌  無數次地用我的身體寫底稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸納構思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很討厭  很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我並不知道煌之外的父親是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛著妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如冰雪般透明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如罪孽般美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  討厭妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  討厭  討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}我  最喜歡的  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污穢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我的面前  消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  我誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重…人格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  明明有兩個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個在醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  妳是死後文的郵遞員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出來的那重人格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的事情全部推給小文  狡猾的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是咧  小文是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  謝謝  美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  洗完澡  畫城堡的畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡裡有王子和公主  晚上有舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有貓小丑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  還有貓頭鷹家庭教師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡食蟻獸女僕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她是個貪吃鬼  總是被甩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河馬軍隊都是貪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都吃  什麼都喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝河馬國  感謝河馬國
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家分給我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌老師一直在虐待自己的女兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼作家  都是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係  那樣寫出的書賣了80萬冊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把醜聞掩蓋下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真幹得出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們畢竟是出版社嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還有點疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人注意到嗎  文歌…妳們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不被允許出家門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒見過煌以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不知道幼兒園  小學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中是第一所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次  被很多人注視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一天到晚待在保健室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…不全是恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人群中  心會疲勞  會緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小文仍然努力呆在學校裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  妳是美歌對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學校的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在腦海的深處注視著她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕你的事也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是因為小文討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是嚇了一跳  不由得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可好了  要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經是初中時的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是因為在意  才這麼拚命找美川嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說姊姊  稍微說下妳妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦斯爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要好好懲罰她不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用哪個好  用哪個好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用哪個好  真難選
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  文歌  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從裡面鎖上的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川  美川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳竟敢打我  明明那樣愛過妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被那樣虐待  小文到最後一刻依然喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也要背叛我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把『美麗』從妳體內趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文會死的 小文會死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}好痛  好痛啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文會死的…小文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再欺負小文了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射殺你的不是小文  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小文深信是自己幹的  封閉了心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經連我的聲音都聽不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該把制裁你的事情交給小文的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是殺了人類  是瞞不過福音局的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰管那些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文有多喜歡你  我就多恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文無法下手  我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  小文她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡  妳們的工作要是被警察知道了會很麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  警察啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒法解釋我們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這個人工作  賺取文歌的住院費
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我也想繼續看這個無藥可救的美川煌寫的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼老師  您會寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我沒有文歌的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不寫  我們會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我努力過了  可是寫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別撒嬌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了一驚  夏香的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊她關鍵時刻很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會做到那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到那樣的文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後不可以有事瞞著我了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是搭檔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了等待那邊的文歌  文伽成了郵遞員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地選這片送信區域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我們約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我們能不能和妳一起等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妳喜歡文歌一樣  我們也很喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也很喜歡她  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  大家


