Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿臉笑容的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南海的光輝中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會


